{
  "stem": "5356.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, because it was half a mile when you walked into the ammunition factory.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you were assigned to this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we worked in three shifts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Every week, we had a different shift-- like from 8:00 till 4:00, or from 4:00 to 11:00, and then from 11:00 til the morning.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's how we were working.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the life was tough, because if you didn't have no means, you had to live on the-- on the food what they gave you.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They gave you a soup.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they gave you, you know, piece of bread and coffee twice a day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My brother and I lived in-- we had a little [INAUDIBLE] in the same [INAUDIBLE]-- you know, there were bunk beds like, you know, [INAUDIBLE] just boards, you know.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And most of the people in the same barrack were from my-- were from my hometown and from another town, from Zwolen.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You know, and we went every day to work, came back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we worked like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "A lot of people died from hunger, typhus.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I mean, I, myself, and my brother were stricken with typhus.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But we had two girls from our hometown what they cooked for us and they nursed us through that time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The both of them are in To-- in Toronto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember their family names now, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they're married, and they have their own children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But both of them live in Toronto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One was [INAUDIBLE] and one was-- the other one was-- I can't even remember her name.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They knew us from home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, we knew them from home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we were neighbors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The city wasn't that big.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they nursed us through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were in Skarzysko till 1944, end of the summer '44.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
